  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\nSometimes the font size is incorrect in the backup seed phrase popup\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Go to Settings -> Appearance\r\n2. Set the theme to Light\r\n3. Set the font size to XS\r\n4. Set the theme to Dark\r\n5. Set the font size to XXL\r\n6. Set the theme back to Light and check the Back up seed phrase\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nFont size used in Back up seed phrase matches the Font size set in the Appearance settings\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nSee the font size set in the background:\r\n<img width=\"1512\" alt=\"Screenshot 2022-11-23 at 12 33 27\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/47811206/203525281-a979555e-d9d4-4b62-9c65-a58e5e5667f4.png\">\r\n\r\nFont size used in Back up seed phrase is the last set Font size for the current theme (XS was last set on Light theme, but the current Font size is XXL)\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version:\r\n- Operating System: MacOs\r\n\r\n",
